#Helpful packages

**Data analyses**
Seurat - all things single cell
SingleR - cell type annotations (use with caution)
immunarch - TCR/BCR repertoire
rstatix - general stats
precrec - ROC
survival - survival analyses
vegan - diversity analsyses (I used for TCR repertoire statistics)
cutpointr - useful for determining cutouffs between groups
fgesa - fast GSEA
DESeq2 - differential expression (RNA-seq)

**ggplot add ons**
patchwork - combining plots
ggsci - journal themed color palates
survminer - survival plots
ggrepel - labels that don't overlap

**Other plots**
ComplexHeatmap - heatmaps 
circlize - circos plots
